{"tid":918822,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「世界百大美女」第二名南韓Clara晃美胸不科學  粉絲們被行走律動「震暈」","createTime":"2018-11-27T13:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T19:55:28.000Z","uid":9573,"like":21,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"445fb603a5421dc640b3605c8af073c103cda1d3","tid":918822,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T13:58:25.000Z","msg":"33歲的南韓女星克拉拉（Clara）曾在2014年被美國《Mode》雜誌評選「世界百大美女」第二名，英國籍的她作風洋派，有著天使臉孔、魔鬼身材也從不藏私，還能講上一口迷人英國腔的英文，不單戲劇中常有比基尼與性感橋段，迷到同劇男演員神魂顛倒，她向來嚴格要求自己身材，不時看到她運動的影片，豐胸翹臀的S曲線超級火辣，更不吝於秀出傲人完美角度，讓粉絲們全都看傻眼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/11/27/1661924-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F11%2F27%2F1661924-XXL.jpg&h=8c04e5fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲擁有火辣曲線的女星克拉拉，向來不吝於在社群平台曬性感照。<br />\n<br />\n她在IG人數也高達一百二十幾萬粉絲追蹤，而克拉拉更時常在IG曬噴血辣照，昨（26日）天她上傳一則正在工作時的花絮影片，只見她穿著一套太古城兩房月租2.05萬中空綁帶黑色馬甲泳裝，只見整個鏡頭角度卻一直放在「俯視角」，走動時晃動美胸「很不科學」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/11/27/1661930-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F11%2F27%2F1661930-XXL.jpg&h=52940707&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲克拉拉昨曬「俯視角」性感影片，走動時晃動胸部「很不科學」。<br />\n<br />\n克拉拉表情相當自信，只見她標籤sunshine，粉絲們不禁喊：「暈了」、「這影片怎麼無止盡？」、「好大...一個日出」、「胸懷大志」、「來勢洶洶，好嚇人」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v900ANQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv900ANQ.jpg&h=051891a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲朱千雪先前活動時讓觀眾看傻眼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/actressclara/videos/261384637885081/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Factressclara%2Fvideos%2F261384637885081%2F&d=CXCMuuhwcMS%2FMedlsEZQiozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=4ebfa952\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/actressclara/videos/261384637885081/</a><br />\n▲克拉拉晃動走錄花絮。"},{"pid":"b71771b9f25019297ee8e9402f9d251c7f610448","tid":918822,"uid":54884,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T14:02:49.000Z","msg":"穿著一套太古城兩房月租2.05萬中空綁帶黑色馬甲泳裝"},{"pid":"0150c4fbf9c6064e166d9c87573acc45ccb9916e","tid":918822,"uid":76098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T14:06:37.000Z","msg":"有咩好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f44e8461f46d81b80a47c18ca4740f2acae1f661","tid":918822,"uid":177089,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b71771b9f25019297ee8e9402f9d251c7f610448","tid":918822,"uid":54884,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T14:02:49.000Z","msg":"穿著一套太古城兩房月租2.05萬中空綁帶黑色馬甲泳裝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T14:12:32.000Z","msg":"著住層樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3037bd91088f97f131fd1d7b3e2782c40dcdca14","tid":918822,"uid":54959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b71771b9f25019297ee8e9402f9d251c7f610448","tid":918822,"uid":54884,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T14:02:49.000Z","msg":"穿著一套太古城兩房月租2.05萬中空綁帶黑色馬甲泳裝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T15:15:09.000Z","msg":"大騎樓"},{"pid":"5ebc9b7a1d6cfa48a9301ee7d53a62c5eb9a6dbf","tid":918822,"uid":73722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T16:46:50.000Z","msg":"▲朱千雪先前活動時讓觀眾看傻眼。"},{"pid":"ef1260f2530af26f5bb48a1bad993173459e514c","tid":918822,"uid":65984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T18:53:09.000Z","msg":"對波死實實咁郁都唔郁下, 你同我講晃動?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc0f087e2572b600c52be10cadb2a322a4ceb70","tid":918822,"uid":179967,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T18:58:09.000Z","msg":"記者老母對波晃緊呀?邊撚度晃呀?"},{"pid":"c446ed63a2bef619c2914c4f714bab03d7b2bdbe","tid":918822,"uid":418